Package <Unnamed>

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CommunicationInterface
    Defines what methods are accessible over RMI
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Controller
    Controller for GUI, handles all changes that user will see, can be updated externally, notifies Messenger of typed messages/commands
    GUI
    Initializes and sets up the GUI, passes the controller to the parent Messenger class
    Messenger
    Entry point for peer-to-peer communication, can wait for connection or initialize a connection, receives messages from connected Messengers or can send messages
    Security
    Handles security related tasks on behalf of Messenger, interacts with the javax.crypto and java.security libraries
